{"tid":2094543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇可能再快樂","createTime":"2020-07-04T17:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:32:07.000Z","uid":51936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04ea7a4bf2de10848d648e88b1892a767d872198","tid":2094543,"uid":51936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"今日應該係慶祝嘅節日，開心唔起<br />\n<br />\n對方問我你係未唔係咁開心，我話唔係<br />\n<br />\n咁點解你好似冇咁開心嘅<br />\n<br />\n我話我個心入邊其實係開心，但個人表現唔出好開心，可能我唔係一個演員<br />\n<br />\n早知你都唔係咁開心唔搞咁多野喇<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，辜負咗你想我開心嘅一番心意<br />\n<br />\nso9ry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216e0944176a2ebe170a89ebfb66275ad2dff6e0","tid":2094543,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"冇mood唔係你既錯"},{"pid":"08dc95c87aa0e1cebc35063d962540631561f719","tid":2094543,"uid":51936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216e0944176a2ebe170a89ebfb66275ad2dff6e0","tid":2094543,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"冇mood唔係你既錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"謝謝你的安慰<br />\n我諗好多香港人都已經返唔返以前<br />\n大家精神都好壓抑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}